457
00:27:28.618 --> 00:27:30.142
Dinheiro.

458
00:27:31.688 --> 00:27:33.349
Trezentos?

459
00:27:34.524 --> 00:27:37.960
Howard, pegue uma laranja.

460
00:27:40.463 --> 00:27:43.132
- Obrigado, Tio Howard.
- Obrigada, Tio Howard.


461
00:27:43.133 --> 00:27:44.998
Obrigada, Howard.

462
00:27:47.771 --> 00:27:49.371
